{
  "stem": "22237.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, the first change was the fact that he wasn't allowed to work openly.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But yes, they had a hard time getting kosher meats.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't allow to-- to-- the meat to be koshered.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and that reminds me of something else also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember being in some kind of a market where my mother used to bought the chicken.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had live chickens then, and there was this what they call [YIDDISH], the person who would kill the chicken.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I remember being there in the market, and somebody came in, a non-Jewish man, big, non-Jewish man.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, your heads will roll like the heads of these chickens roll.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I remember I couldn't sleep for a long time after I heard him say that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that just-- just came to me as you asked me that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there are other laws.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At this point, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember being-- not being able to work because we couldn't get the kosher meat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And times were just getting very bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then meanwhile, relatives and friends would leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We already heard people leave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were-- as happy as we were for them, it was like going to the street and you met another Jewish person, you would say, where are you going?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So do you have anything?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were always so interested in finding out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes people said, I don't know what we are going to do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We tried this country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We tried that country.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, sometimes people would say, yes, we are leaving tomorrow for such and such a place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and as happy as we were for these people, we always wished that we would be in their places.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how-- how we wanted to leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
